description:
For an international project in Chennai, we are urgently looking for a Full Remote Senior Full\\-Stack .NET/Angular Developer with \\+5/\\+10 years of professional experience. The selected candidate will work as part of the development team and report to the project manager and technical leads.










 We are looking for a motivated contractor. Candidates need to be fluent in English.










**Tasks and responsibilities:** 



* Developing APIs to handle the business processes;
* Building of applications intended for managing transaction and reporting capabilities;
* Collaborate with angular team for integration;
* Building of data feed APIs to be consumed by other applications;
* Deployment of the application into the cloud environment;
* Developing front end application screens;
* Building of applications intended for managing transaction and reporting capabilities;
* Collaborate with .Net team for integration;
* Deployment of the application into the cloud environment;









**Profile:** 



* Bachelor or Master degree;
* \\+5 years of .NET development experience;
* Strong expertise in Angular and .NET technologies;
* Should have worked in production support engagements;
* Knowledge and hands\\-on experience in Azure Cloud;
* Fluent in English;
